lue\\\")).isEqualTo(3);\\n        } catch (Error error) {\\n            if (!isUnsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading(error)) {\\n                throw error;\\n            }\\n        } catch (RuntimeException exception) {\\n            if (!isUnsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading(exception)) {\\n                throw exception;\\n            }\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    private static boolean isUnsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading(Throwable throwable) {\\n        Throwable current = throwable;\\n        while (current != null) {\\n            if (current instanceof Error && NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError((Error) current)) {\\n                return true;\\n            }\\n            current = current.getCause();\\n        }\\n        return false;\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1674, \"output\": 1209, \"cacheRead\": 20992, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 23875, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\", \"timestamp\": 1777711302976, \"responseId\": \"resp_0104e4ee87262e220169f5b8c772cc819c99c2a60016df67d6\"}}\n[tool-exec] start id=call_l7kivYbOmOwbhxeMtZo7NlEI|fc_0104e4ee87262e220169f5b8d00668819c92ebc844e43fcd02 name=write args={\"path\": \"tests/src/cglib/cglib-nodep/2.2.2/src/test/java/cglib/cglib_nodep/StringSwitcherTest.java\", \"content\": \"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npackage cglib.cglib_nodep;\\n\\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\\n\\nimport net.sf.cglib.util.StringSwitcher;\\nimport org.graalvm.internal.tck.NativeImageSupport;\\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\\n\\npublic class StringSwitcherTest {\\n    @Test\\n    void mapsKnownStringsAndRetu